Privacy Policy for Future Baby iOS App
At OriginX, ensuring the privacy and security of your personal data is our foremost commitment. This Privacy Policy delineates our approach to collecting, using, and safeguarding your personal information when you use our
Future Baby
iOS app.
Information Collection: Our
Future Baby
iOS app may collect specific personal details from you, including your name, email address, device specifics (such as type, operating system, and ID), and data related to your app usage.
Information Usage: Your personal data may be used for various purposes, such as delivering the
Future Baby
iOS app and its features, communicating with you about your app usage, personalizing your app experience with recommendations, and improving the app and its features.
Information Sharing: We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes. However, we may disclose your data to third-party service providers assisting us with the app, under contractual obligations to protect your information and limit its use. Additionally, we may disclose your information if legally required, to enforce our policies, or to protect our or others' rights, property, or safety.
Data Security: We employ reasonable security measures to protect your personal data from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no internet or electronic storage method is entirely secure.
Third-Party Service Providers: We share your data with third-party vendors and service providers who perform tasks on our behalf, under strict contracts to protect your personal information. They are prohibited from misusing your data and must comply with our specified data retention periods. For example, we use Google Cloud Platform for cloud computing services.
Business Transfers: In circumstances such as mergers, asset sales, financing, or business acquisitions, we may transfer your information to another entity.
Face Data Usage: The collection of facial data is solely for executing baby face generation operations.
Data Retention and Deletion: Facial data is retained for a limited time, such as 24 hours, and then permanently deleted. We do not retain any face data once your baby face has been generated. All personal data is immediately deleted from our system to ensure your privacy and data security.
Data Handling:
Future Baby
processes facial images or photos uploaded by users for baby generation and image enhancement, using Google Cloud for processing. Uploaded images are deleted after processing. We collect face data from the images you upload solely to generate your requested avatars. This data is not used for any other purposes. Our face data is processed in real-time to create avatars and is not stored or shared with any third parties.
Your Rights: You can access, correct, update, or delete your personal information at any time by contacting us at hello@originx.app.
Policy Updates: We may modify this Privacy Policy periodically and will notify you of significant changes through our website or app.
Contact: For inquiries regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at hello@originx.app, and we will promptly address your concerns.